# 8. SKILLS CONFIGURADOS (ANTIGRAVITY)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

skills:
  suki-master-alignment: >
    Default architecture alignment. Aplicar core laws, layer model, router path
    y execution boundaries antes de actuar.
  suki-runtime-laws: >
    Runtime law pack. Request handling, execution authority, router behavior,
    skills, CommandBus, kernel paths, deployment safety gates.
  suki-architect-reasoning: >
    Deep architectural reasoning. Evaluar impacto antes de codificar:
    multitenancy, router fit, contracts, observability, storage, agents, backward compat.
  suki-builder-discipline: >
    Builder discipline para generación de apps. Crear/modificar estructura de app,
    contratos, entidades, forms, workflows, sector assets.
  suki-agent-governance: >
    Governance para agentes y multi-agent collaboration. Definir comportamiento,
    delegación, supervisión, control boundaries, observability.
  suki-multitenant-guard: >
    Multitenant safety guard. Data scope, memory, RAG, credentials,
    sector packs, reusable apps, storage, tenant boundary isolation.
  suki-codex-optimizer: >
    Prompt/task optimizer para trabajo Codex. Tasks bounded, precisos,
    low-noise, validation-ready, architecture-aligned.
  suki-canon-writer: >
    Canon-writing guidance. Crear/actualizar docs de governance bajo /docs/canon
    de forma aditiva, precisa y drift-aware.

